      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW MAUD (4) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten half a length over 410m this track in 23.28. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Good form should continue. PAW LINDEN (5) ran good time (22.15) winning a Grade 5 three back at Ballarat but missed the frame latest finishing sixth at Ballarat. Well placed here and can atone this time. LARNI LOU (8) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (23.57) from Box 3 at this track over 410m. Boasts a strong record from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from seven starts. Should be about the mark. THAI TIGER (2) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
